"конкретной кампании. При редакции письма, наоборот, можно менять только "
"текст писма, хедер и футер как часть шаблона менять нельзя."
msgstr ""
"When editing a template you can change only the email header and footer. The "
"email body text is a placeholder — for an actual send it will be replaced "
"with the message text of the specific campaign. When editing an email, "
"conversely, you can change only the email body; the header and footer as "
"part of the template cannot be changed."

